OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome brightness across the
OL,6,Fnortheast at times, especially this
OL,7,Fmorning. Otherwise it will be cloudy
OL,8,Fwith patchy rain, this mainly across
OL,9,Fthe south and east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,12,Fwith patchy rain. Then the rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will be cloudy with rain
OL,14,Fspreading to the west coast, but dry
OL,15,Felsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
