OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy with rain across the
OL,6,Fwest in the morning, this spreading
OL,7,Facross eastern parts in the afternoon.
OL,8,FTurning drier across the west through
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Mild around Inverness
OL,10,Fand Nairn.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry with
OL,13,Fsome bright or sunny spells on Friday
OL,14,Fand Saturday, becoming windy in the
OL,15,Ffar northwest. Cloudy on Sunday with
OL,16,Foccasional rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
